document_data.name: Vil'Kenna
document_data.mainbody:
'''Vil'Kenna''' was a female [[barbarian]] from the [[Sky Pony tribe]] of [[Uthgardt]] barbarians. In [[1374 DR]] she traveled to [[Nesmé]] on the edge of the [[Evermoors]] to join others from her tribe who had been hired by First Speaker [[Tessarin Alaurin]] to defend the city against [[troll]] and [[giant]] attack.{{Cite dungeon/144/The Muster of Morach Tor|18}}
